name: Interdimensional Immigrator
description:
Story

After an inhibitor failure during a prototype testing, your ship is sent flying through alternate realities!

Strap into your Phaser Fighter and get ready to brave your way through dimensions to make it home!

Instructions

Avoid debris as you find enough blue matter cells to jump to the next dimension!

Press escape to return to the menu at any time.

Created by Tim for Mini Game Jam #77
